"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/FInYE2k5QIsZUnBXi137D.png?height=2323&width=1670)\\n\\n\\n---\\n\\n## A little about “eschatology”\\n\\nYears before I heard there was a chain to be *on*, I was irked by the immutability of our digital detritus — more immortal than the soul.\\n\\nOr maybe I was haunted by my own eventual traces?\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/vbuAUWaN2hMfxNDzHbOLx.gif?height=300&width=1080)\\n\\nIt turned into the poem above ↑\\n\\n“Eschatology” was originally published in *[Poetry Northwest](https://www.poetrynw.org/).*\\n\\nIt re-appeared on *Poetry Daily* and was printed in my own chapbook ***I Say Potato, You Say Apocalypse***. This is the first time I’ve properly parked it online though. So it’s official; and it’s an NFT!\\n\\nWanna drive it home?\\n\\nThe [RISOGRAPH](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Risograph) lettering was made by [Anna O](https://www.annaoprints.com/) and [Doug Von](https://www.dougvon.com/) — who also did the layout, design, and typesetting for all the poems in my chapbook.\\n\\nThey’re rad people.\\n\\n\\n---\\n\\n### A little about me\\n\\nI make music.\\n\\nbut I’m gonna skip all that for now, since you’re here for a poem. So poems…\\n\\nI’m the winner of Boulevard’s Poetry Prize for Emerging Writers and the recipient of a Maine Literary Award in Poetry. I was selected by former US poet laureate Robert Pinsky as a finalist for the Dorset Prize, and I’ve served as a visiting editor for the Beloit Poetry Journal.\\n\\n**My poems have appeared in:**\\n\\n* POETRY Magazine\\n* The Poetry Review\\n* Prairie Schooner\\n* Poetry Northwest\\n* Beloit Poetry Journal\\n* The Cincinnati Review\\n* Cimarron Review\\n* RHINO\\n* Magma Poetry\\n* Boulevard\\n* Arsenic Lobster\\n* Pacifica Literary Review\\n* Port City Poets (Anthology)\\n* Maine Arts Journal\\n* And more\\n\\nI’ve performed my poems at a number of reading series, including Literary Death Match, Stone Boat, Local Buzz, The Maine Historical Society’s Summer Garden Series, the Belfast Poetry Festival, and more.\\n\\nI’m new to this whole “web3” world, but racing to catch up fast. Figured Mirror would be a good place to put some of these little word machines. Thanks for reading.\\n\\nMore $oon.\\n\\n\\n---\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/1DcXhOe74krTFbKHpOAkk.gif?height=400&width=700)\\n\\n[site](https://www.chrisrobley.com/) | [twitter](https://twitter.com/chrisrobley) | [eels](http://eelslap.com/)\",\"timestamp\":1641963921,\"title\":\"\\\"eschatology\\\" (poem)\"},\"digest\":\"1xPxWQY5N7jy2OaKacU7tnHBVZhboKQlWU4UptqWJGU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xED6082bA132032b888b1028f56d86F341b915138\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"1L9JzUC4-f1qjw0VR_B4jBYEnqMde4RzIZedmiOZWs0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"cTBB-CixOBx5XzxriX6ITrGY41H4p7Tl_bOeG4jpsNA\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"2YTCzSO0dCDhxHZ0seyHCvC7Aj0eXdOLAxUnqprDBgMV_9q12QeqiuSK0a3JDmVGVRScWuXodNTmz8383O6Mww\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x42f305dee85fedf2c7c70187f4351959b80c54b77a318721265d9edb2d668efb170352d26c382c1c7c96aebe5bbecd2a74e9d985d2679fae1ebc240468c94aa61c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"1L9JzUC4-f1qjw0VR_B4jBYEnqMde4RzIZedmiOZWs0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"cTBB-CixOBx5XzxriX6ITrGY41H4p7Tl_bOeG4jpsNA\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"F8LyvLymx2dTz-VQvXnbOsaENatSLBn88M4jHJVaOLw\"}"